"Open the primary domain to see and accept the incoming request under the "
"**Connections** tab."
msgstr "기본 도메인을 열고 **Connections** 탭에서 들어오는 요청을 확인하고 수락하세요."

#: ../../source/deploy/backup-disaster-recovery.rst:191
